snippet.title: Battlefield 1943 Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Battlefield 1943 Available Now for Download!  A full-fledged Battlefield experience featuring boats, tanks, jeeps and dog-fighting airplanes.  The Battle for the Pacific has begun so enlist now for only $14.99 or 1200 MS Points.  More info here: www.battlefield1943.com
